## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
mvn test

# Run tests with specific environment
mvn test -Denv=qa

# Run tests in headed mode (see browser)
mvn test -Dheadless=false

# Run specific test suite
mvn test -DsuiteXmlFile=testng.xml
```

