## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| Browser not found | Run `mvn exec:java -e -D exec.mainClass=com.microsoft.playwright.CLI -D exec.args="install"` |
| Element not found | Check your CSS selectors in page objects match your app |
| Login fails | Verify credentials in config file and selectors in LoginPage |
| Timeout errors | Increase `timeout` value in properties file |
